[[File:Black Guard (1) chathead.png|left]]
'''Black Guards''' are members of the [[Dwarven Black Guard]] found throughout areas controlled by the [[Dwarven Realm]]. They give [[Slayer]] [[experience]] if players are [[Slayer task|assigned]] to kill [[Dwarf|dwarves]]. They wield [[black warhammer]]s, however the black guard in [[Keldagrim]] attack with them much faster than a normal [[warhammer]].
:'''Note:''' The Black Guards located near [[Ice Mountain]] have a limited chance of dropping dwarven loot. Refer to [[Dwarf#Drops|dwarf drop information]] if this is of interest to you.

